      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/kfc-malaysia-temporarily-shutters-outlets-citing-challenging-economy-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[馬來西亞肯德基以經濟形勢嚴峻為由，暫時關閉了在該國的門市，此前當地媒體報道稱，該快餐連鎖店因與以色列有聯繫而遭到抵制。]]></description>
